\ref .0001
\ELANBegin 00:00:00.000
\ELANEnd 00:00:01.500
\ELANParticipant segmentheader
\cm  this annotation file consists of three different segments which were worked on seperately and are at different stages of processing.
The first two segments are continuous in time with no break in between, while the third segment comes from a different tape. That is, although the three segments follow immediately after each other in this file (and in the media files) there is in fact a major break in between segment 2 and 3, necessitated by the need to change tapes in the camera. The part missing in between these two segments is the first segment in the file sukufoun_day1_DAT.wav (DAT recorder was switched on while changing tapes).

The first segment, which starts here, was orginally called:
Sukufoun1_wmmb_vdp_29Mar03_0l 
Transkripsi MB NH/
Port and Engl free translation by AT/
\dt 24/Mar/2007
 

